{"an7.5:0.1":"Anguttara Nikaya 7.5 ","an7.5:0.2":"1. Dhanavagga ","an7.5:0.3":"Sankhittadhanasutta ","an7.5:1.1":"“Sattimani, bhikkhave, dhanani. ","an7.5:1.2":"Katamani satta? ","an7.5:1.3":"Saddhadhanam, siladhanam, hiridhanam, ottappadhanam, sutadhanam, cagadhanam, pannadhanam. ","an7.5:1.4":"Imani kho, bhikkhave, satta dhananiti. ","an7.5:2.1":"Saddhadhanam siladhanam, ","an7.5:2.2":"hiri ottappiyam dhanam; ","an7.5:2.3":"Sutadhananca cago ca, ","an7.5:2.4":"panna ve sattamam dhanam. ","an7.5:3.1":"Yassa ete dhana atthi, ","an7.5:3.2":"itthiya purisassa va; ","an7.5:3.3":"Adaliddoti tam ahu, ","an7.5:3.4":"amogham tassa jivitam. ","an7.5:4.1":"Tasma saddhanca silanca, ","an7.5:4.2":"Pasadam dhammadassanam; ","an7.5:4.3":"Anuyunjetha medhavi, ","an7.5:4.4":"Saram buddhana sasanan”ti. ","an7.5:4.5":"Pancamam. "}